"function cost_f_fast(xs, ys, ws, hs, x, y, w, h, R)
    x1 = x - w/2
    y1 = y - h/2
    x2 = x + w/2
    y2 = y + h/2

    x1s = xs .- ws ./ 2
    y1s = ys .- hs ./ 2

    x2s = xs .+ ws ./ 2
    y2s = ys .+ hs ./ 2

    return sum((x1s .< x2) .& (y1s .< y2) .& (x2s .> x1) .& (y2s .> y1))
end"
